msgctxt "sn37.15:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 37 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 37 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn37.15:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyapeyyālavagga "
msgstr "2. Abbreviated Texts "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 15. Akkodhanasutta → akodhano (pts1)
msgctxt "sn37.15:0.3"
msgid "15. Akkodhanasutta "
msgstr "15. Loving "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn37.15:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā anuruddho yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā … pe … ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā anuruddho bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Venerable Anuruddha went up to the Buddha … and asked him, "

msgctxt "sn37.15:1.2"
msgid "“idhāhaṃ, bhante, mātugāmaṃ passāmi dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjantaṃ. "
msgstr "“Sometimes, sir, with my clairvoyance that’s purified and superhuman, I see that a female—when her body breaks up, after death—is reborn in a good place, a heavenly realm. "

msgctxt "sn37.15:1.3"
msgid "Katīhi nu kho, bhante, dhammehi samannāgato mātugāmo kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjatī”ti? "
msgstr "How many qualities do females have so that they’re reborn in a good place, a heavenly realm?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.244, sc2
msgctxt "sn37.15:2.1"
msgid "“Pañcahi kho, anuruddha, dhammehi samannāgato mātugāmo kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjati. "
msgstr "“Anuruddha, when females have five qualities, when their body breaks up, after death, they are reborn in a good place, a heavenly realm. "

msgctxt "sn37.15:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi? "
msgstr "What five? "

#. VAR: akkodhano → akodhano (pts1)
msgctxt "sn37.15:2.3"
msgid "Saddho ca hoti, hirimā ca hoti, ottappī ca hoti, akkodhano ca hoti, paññavā ca hoti—"
msgstr "They’re faithful, conscientious, prudent, loving, and wise. "

msgctxt "sn37.15:2.4"
msgid "imehi kho, anuruddha, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato mātugāmo kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjatī”ti. "
msgstr "When females have these five qualities, when their body breaks up, after death, they are reborn in a good place, a heavenly realm.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn37.15:2.5"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

